    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and the interior still has that wonderful new-car smell. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
