    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering precise power via six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously maintained to ensure perfect cam phasing, while the chassis remains factory-rigid with documented rear subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein damping, offering exceptional lateral stability and tactile feedback. Free of fluid seepage or thermal cycling fatigue, this is a mechanically flawless, concours-ready drivetrain.",
      "price": 46500.0,
