      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This collector-grade example has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and displays a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in a time-capsule state, featuring supple leather with no bolster wear and that distinct factory-fresh aroma. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, and the mechanicals have been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a comprehensive binder of service records. This car comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
