      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s basically brand new and has been treated like a member of the family since day one. There isn't a single scratch, dent, or smudge to be found\u2014it\u2019s absolutely flawless inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s in perfect shape and ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
