      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its high-pressure VANOS system fully overhauled. This chassis remains structurally pristine with proactive subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Every bushing has been replaced with OEM-plus polyurethane, and the suspension utilizes Bilstein B16 coilovers for precise damping. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, free of synchro wear. Finished in Carbon Black with flawless Laguna Seca Blue leather, this unit shows no bolster wear or UV damage. A rare, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
